6
00:01:05,978 --> 00:01:23,650
Doubtless one leading reason why the world declines honoring us whalemen is this they think that, at best, our vocation amounts to a butchering sort of business, and that when actively engaged therein we are surrounded by all manner of defilements.

7
00:01:23,630 --> 00:01:26,053
Butchers we are, that is true.

8
00:01:26,754 --> 00:01:35,483
But butchers also, and butchers of the bloodiest badge, have been all Mortial commanders whom the world invariably delights to honor.

9
00:01:35,744 --> 00:01:51,882
