38
00:05:56,640 --> 00:06:01,286
All that is made such a flourish of in the old South Sea voyages.

39
00:06:01,606 --> 00:06:06,913
Those things were but the lifetime commonplaces of our heroic Nantucketers.

40
00:06:06,893 --> 00:06:16,265
